    <p><anchor n="T.50.2059.0392c08"/><lb ed="T" n="0392c08"/><persName key="A002290">釋法朗</persName>，<placeName key="PL000000047474">高昌</placeName>人。幼而執行精苦，多諸徵瑞，韜<lb ed="T" n="0392c09"/>光蘊德，人莫測其所階。<persName key="A002290">朗</persName>師<persName key="A003271">釋法進</persName>亦高<lb ed="T" n="0392c10"/>行沙門。<persName key="A003271">進</persName>嘗閉戶獨坐，忽見<persName key="A002290">朗</persName>在前，問從<lb ed="T" n="0392c11"/>何處來？答云：「從戶鑰中入。」云：「與遠僧俱<lb ed="T" n="0392c12"/>至，日既將中，願為設食。」<persName key="A003271">進</persName>即為設食，唯聞<lb ed="T" n="0392c13"/>匕鉢之聲，竟不見人。昔<placeName key="PL000000018775">廬山</placeName><persName key="A001204">慧遠</persName>嘗以一<lb ed="T" n="0392c14"/>袈裟遺<persName key="A003271">進</persName>，<persName key="A003271">進</persName><persName key="A002290">朗</persName>以為嚫。<persName key="A002290">朗</persName>云：「眾僧已去，別<lb ed="T" n="0392c15"/>日當取之。」後見執爨者就進取衣，<persName key="A003271">進</persName>即與<lb ed="T" n="0392c16"/>之。訪常執爨者，皆云不取，方知是先聖人<lb ed="T" n="0392c17"/>權迹取也。至<persName key="A002596">魏虜</persName>毀滅佛法，<persName key="A002290">朗</persName>西適<placeName key="PL000000047823">龜茲</placeName>。<lb ed="T" n="0392c18"/>龜茲王與彼國大禪師結約：「若有得道者<lb ed="T" n="0392c19"/>至，當為我說，我當供養。」及<persName key="A002290">朗</persName>至，乃以白<lb ed="T" n="0392c20"/>王，王待以聖禮。後終於<placeName key="PL000000047823">龜茲</placeName>。焚屍之日，兩<lb ed="T" n="0392c21"/><ptr target="fn21"/>眉湧泉直上于天。眾歎希有，收骨起塔。<lb ed="T" n="0392c22"/>後<placeName key="PL000000047439">西域</placeName>人來<ptr target="fn22"/>北土，具傳此事。</p><p>時<placeName key="PL000000045053">涼州</placeName>復有<lb ed="T" n="0392c23"/>沙門<persName key="A003272">智整</persName>，亦貞苦有異行，為<ptr target="fn23"/>[系-小]主<persName key="A003273">楊難當</persName><lb ed="T" n="0392c24"/>所事。後入<placeName key="PL000000046535">寒峽</placeName>山石穴中不<ptr target="fn24"/>返。</p>
